					"markdown": "BluetoothRestarter is meant to be used if you are experiencing problems with not recieving notifications on bluetooth devices after doing a respring.\nIt works by turning airplane mode on for 3 seconds and turns it back off right after the device resprings.\nThis should cause bluetooth to turn off and turn back on, which fixes the issue."
